# Retail Sales & Profitability Analysis

## Business Problem
The retail business lacked clarity on sales performance, product profitability, and revenue trends.
This project analyzes retail transaction data to identify revenue drivers, profit gaps, and key sales patterns to support better business decisions.

## Tools Used
- Python (pandas, NumPy)
- SQL (MySQL)
- Power BI

## Key Tasks Performed
- Cleaned and preprocessed retail sales data using Python.
- Answered 18+ business-driven questions using SQL involving aggregations, CASE statements, and grouping.
- Built a one-page Power BI dashboard to visualize KPIs, sales trends, and product performance.

## Project Assets
- Project Report (PDF): included in repository
- Python Script: included in repository
- SQL Queries: included in repository
- Power BI Dashboard: included in repository

## Outcome
The analysis highlighted high-performing products, profit-driving categories, and loss-making areas, enabling actionable insights for improving profitability and sales strategy.
